    "message": "Created successfully!\nServer: $SERVER$\nChannel name: $NAME$\nChannel key: $KEY$\n\nThe key has been saved in this extension automatically, but you should also back it up somewhere safe (e.g. a password manager) — the server will never show this plaintext key again.",
